name: Archives - 03 - Anonymous smoker in Hackney, London, on 19/09/2004
description: Photo taken on September 19th 2004 in London, during the “Shoreditch Festival and Car Free Day”. One physical copy of this, printed on Dibond, exists somewhere in Italy. Shot with a Sony DSC-T1 pocket-sized camera by Matteo Manzini @matteomanzini__ (Twitter/Instagram). “Still based in Milan but travelling back and forth, I was doing a lot of people watching around East London at that time, trying to take visual notes of the highlights.”.
